《'''紅衣小女孩2'''》（{{lang-en|''The Tag-Along 2''}}），是一部改編自台灣家喻戶曉的[[都會傳奇|都市傳說]]、靈異事件「[[紅衣小女孩|紅衣小女孩]]」的同名電影《[[紅衣小女孩_(電影)|紅衣小女孩]]》的續集 ，為《紅衣小女孩》三部曲第二部。 由[[楊丞琳|楊丞琳]]、[[許瑋甯|許瑋甯]]、[[高慧君|高慧君]]、[[龍劭華|龍劭華]]、 [[黃河_(台灣演員)|黃河]]主演<ref>{{cite news |title=「紅衣小女孩2」最恐怖的原來是… |newspaper=[[聯合報|聯合報]] |url = http://udn.com/news/story/8/2146122 |date=2016-12-03 |author=蘇詠智 |access-date=2016-12-07 |language=zh-TW |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161204124914/http://udn.com/news/story/8/2146122 |archive-date=2016-12-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title = 許瑋甯談重機騎士　臭臉說：我不是阮經天代表！|publisher=今日新聞 |url = http://www.nownews.com/n/2016/12/03/2326649 |author=翁新涵 |access-date=2016-12-07 |language=zh-TW |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161206042556/http://www.nownews.com/n/2016/12/03/2326649 |archive-date=2016-12-06|dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=楊丞琳素顏演鬼片 許瑋甯變皮包骨 |agency = 中央社 |url = http://www.cna.com.tw/news/amov/201612030251-1.aspx |author=王靖怡|access-date=2016-12-07|language=zh-TW |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161204125315/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/amov/201612030251-1.aspx |archive-date=2016-12-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title = 金馬逐后失利 許瑋甯喊話：會沒有極限的努力 |newspaper = [[自由時報|自由時報]] |url = http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1905766 |author=高睿希 |access-date=2016-12-07 |language=zh-TW |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161203142527/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1905766 |archive-date=2016-12-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title = 續攤《紅衣小女孩》剃光眉毛 許瑋甯：我不是小天代理人 |newspaper=[[中國時報|中國時報]] |url = http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20161204000464-260112 |date=2016-12-04 |author1 = 潘鈺楨 |author2 = 洪秀瑛 |access-date=2016-12-07 |language=zh-TW |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161204125643/http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20161204000464-260112 |archive-date=2016-12-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title = 膽小許瑋甯3演驚悚片　竟是為了愛他 |newspaper=蘋果日報 |url = http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/a